snippet.title: Mario Kart 8 Deluxe - Booster Course Pass Wave 6 - Nintendo Switch 9.14.2023
snippet.description:
The final wave of the Mario Kart 8 Deluxe – Booster Course Pass arrives this holiday! Learn more: https://mariokart8.nintendo.com/booster-course-pass/

Wave 6 includes Daisy Circuit plus 7 more courses, along with 4 returning playable characters:

- Diddy Kong
- Funky Kong
- Pauline
- Peachette

#MarioKart #NintendoSwitch #NintendoDirect
